{"tid":2186982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高登爆炸頭訪問左負責檢疫護士 : 連鼻腔都掂唔到 根本唔會準確 !","createTime":"2020-09-03T10:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T12:57:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5e01f0e4eef961f506cbc48fe225372d381c294e","tid":2186982,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:41:09.000Z","msg":"【1cm ？我撩鼻屎都深過佢】【高登訪問】<br />\n<br />\n全民檢測已進行3天，本報得到一份採樣工作人員的內部指引。當中指示鼻腔拭子採樣只需插入鼻孔1-2cm，而不是鼻咽拭子般深入鼻咽位置20cm 。<br />\n<br />\n鼻咽拭子需要用長檢驗棒深入鼻咽可達20 cm，可達外耳道口。但政府「全文檢測」卻只有鼻孔1-2cm深。（圖二）<br />\n<br />\n負責採樣的護士表示「我撩鼻屎都深過佢」，「根本連鼻腔都未到莫講話係鼻咽」，「根本唔準」，覺得政府想「做個樣撩下就算」。<br />\n<br />\n近日有報道訪問被採樣的市民表示過程並不會造成任何不適。另一護士則表示：「緊係啦，求其做好淺，上面暗示哂唔比我地真做搞到佢地唔舒服」。更質疑整個「全文檢測」只是政府私相授受利益輸送的幌子，「假陰性仲大鑊，中咗招以為冇事」。<br />\n<br />\n記者：爆炸頭￼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高登新聞部需要你嘅支持<br />\n<br />\nPayme：<a href=\"https://qr.payme.hsbc.com.hk/2/EHXFoABoMJH1422DuwMCPF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqr.payme.hsbc.com.hk%2F2%2FEHXFoABoMJH1422DuwMCPF&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=4d3028fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qr.payme.hsbc.com.hk/2/EHXFoABoMJH1422DuwMCPF</a><br />\nFPS：2834836（Alive ! Media &amp; Communications Limited）<br />\nPaypal：<a href=\"https://www.paypal.me/hkgolden?country.x=HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.me%2Fhkgolden%3Fcountry.x%3DHK&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=8e8ee0f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.paypal.me/hkgolden?country.x=HK</a><br />\n銀行帳戶：Alive ! Media &amp; Communications Limited<br />\nHang Seng Bank Account 254-8-055066<br />\n<br />\n如果想支持高登記者，歡迎大家以單次／月費贊助形式捐款畀我哋。<br />\n詳情請至：<a href=\"https://news.hkgolden.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.hkgolden.com&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=15a19c24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.hkgolden.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/116178588425696/posts/3395435210500001/?extid=5pIYRRVxPrg2zUkz&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F116178588425696%2Fposts%2F3395435210500001%2F%3Fextid%3D5pIYRRVxPrg2zUkz%26d%3Dn&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=f52ff6a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/116178588425696/posts/3395435210500001/?extid=5pIYRRVxPrg2zUkz&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"a86d50e308c1f07127afe6f62798079a6dc4dcd8","tid":2186982,"uid":51753,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"有人話隊到 好深"},{"pid":"7e0545878901b9a287b6f97c6be6b7142b0e0b57","tid":2186982,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:43:28.000Z","msg":"（圖二）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a804e17f4a1319236b6337997449ae841dc84034","tid":2186982,"uid":277187,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"隔離有po有議員驗完流鼻血流到返屋企"},{"pid":"c45d2fe2c8ac9805f6abc66825237d5aa1f2c19e","tid":2186982,"uid":365791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:47:10.000Z","msg":"根本係撩鼻屎，正常冇病徵1-2cm果到可以撩到咩分泌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撩到鼻屎/鼻毛就有"},{"pid":"5a1b874760315e1be9dc9a4e6c5dce6ec3888ba6","tid":2186982,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a804e17f4a1319236b6337997449ae841dc84034","tid":2186982,"uid":277187,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"隔離有po有議員驗完流鼻血流到返屋企"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"dc7f5f12a0414b3835e5847dc48cf018252f6358","tid":2186982,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c45d2fe2c8ac9805f6abc66825237d5aa1f2c19e","tid":2186982,"uid":365791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor